@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@memberToken = paste-member-token-here
@adminToken = paste-admin-token-here

### Security headers are present
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books

### Login as member
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "member@books.test",
  "password": "password"
}

### Login as admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@books.test",
  "password": "password"
}

### Rate limit test - run 6 times with wrong password
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@books.test",
  "password": "wrong"
}

### Current user
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}

### Validation test - future year should fail
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/books
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Future Book",
  "author": "X",
  "year": 9999
}

### XSS-safe JSON test
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/books
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "<script>alert('hi')</script>",
  "author": "X",
  "year": 2024
}

### Member IDOR test - book 1 belongs to admin, expect 403
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/books/1
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Hijacked"
}

### Admin can update any book
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/books/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Admin Updated"
}

### Member delete should fail with 403
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/books/2
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}

### Admin delete should pass
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/books/2
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### CORS allowed origin
OPTIONS {{baseUrl}}/api/books
Origin: http://localhost:5173

### CORS unknown origin
OPTIONS {{baseUrl}}/api/books
Origin: http://attacker.example

### Admin audit log
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/audit
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
